title: MasterClass - Neil Gaiman - The Art of Storytelling
description: MasterClass - Neil Gaiman - The Art of Storytelling https://www.masterclass.com/classes/neil-gaiman-teaches-the-art-of-storytelling Unleash your imagination Award-winning author Neil Gaiman has spent more than a quarter of a century crafting vivid, absorbing fiction. Now, the author of Stardust, Coraline, and The Sandman teaches his approach to imaginative storytelling. Learn how to find your unique voice, develop original ideas, and breathe life into your characters. Discover Neil’s philosophy on what drives a story—and open new windows to the stories inside you
